<h1 id="slovak-language-for-business-central" sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="14">Slovak language for Business Central</h1>

<blockquote sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="16">
<p sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="16">Update 31.05.2024</p>
</blockquote>
<p sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="18">This help will help you set up Business Central in Slovak language.</p>
<p sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">To change the language, follow this procedure:</p>
<ol sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">
<li sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">Install <strong sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">SK language pack</strong> app.</li>
<li sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="23">Run and log into Business Central.</li>
<li sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="24">Open <strong sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="24">Purchase of an ARICOMA product</strong> page and activate <strong sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="24">SK language pack</strong> (mandatory for next update)</li>
<li sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="25">Click on <strong sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="25">Settings</strong> icon, select <strong sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="25">My Settings</strong> and change language to: &quot;Slovak&quot;.</li>
<li sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">After Business Central refresh is finished, your Business Central is in Slovak.</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29"><a href="solutions.html" sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29">ARICOMA Řešení</a><br>
<a href="sk-legislative-pack.html" sourcefile="Solutions/sk-language.md" sourcestartlinenumber="30">SK Legislativní balíček</a></p>
